title: Forestburg Independent School District
text:
Forestburg Independent School District is a public <a href="school%20district">school district</a> based in the community of <a href="Forestburg%2C%20Texas">Forestburg</a>, <a href="Texas">Texas</a> (<a href="United%20States">USA</a>).
The district has one school <a href="Forestburg%20High%20School">Forestburg School</a> that serves students in grades pre-kindergarten through twelve.
Academic achievement.
In 2009, the school district was rated "<a href="Texas%20Education%20Agency%20accountability%20ratings%20system">recognized</a>" by the <a href="Texas%20Education%20Agency">Texas Education Agency</a>.
Special programs.
Athletics.
Forestburg High School High School plays <a href="six-man%20football">six-man football</a>.
